<h2 class="h3 fw-bold mb-4">How we operate and why players choose <span class="text-primary fw-black">Robopragma Pro</span></h2>

<h3 class="h5 fw-bold mt-4 mb-3">Account security and verification</h3>
<p class="mb-3">We require account verification before your first withdrawal. You provide your national ID (KTP), proof of address (utility bill or bank statement), and a selfie holding your ID. This process typically takes a few hours to one business day. KYC (Know Your Customer) verification is mandatory under Indonesian financial regulations and protects both you and our platform. Once verified, you can withdraw winnings to your payment method without further delays.</p>

<h3 class="h5 fw-bold mt-4 mb-3">Live-dealer production quality</h3>
<p class="mb-3">Our Robopragma Pro live tables are produced to broadcast standards. Each studio features professional lighting, multiple camera angles, and HD video encoding. Dealers are trained, multilingual, and follow strict protocols. Table limits are transparent—you see the minimum and maximum bet before joining. Our live-dealer portfolio is audited regularly to ensure fairness and compliance with local regulations.</p>

