<p class="mb-3">We support multiple payment methods so you can fund your account via your preferred channel. DANA, e-wallet, mobile banking, and local payment are popular for mobile users. online payment and e-wallet offer alternative routes. Direct bank transfers (mobile banking, local payment, online payment, e-wallet) are available for larger deposits. Withdrawals process through the same method you used to deposit. During peak periods (e.g., after Liga 1 matches or around Idul Fitri and Idul Adha holidays), withdrawal review may take slightly longer, but we aim for standard business-hour processing.</p>

<h3 class="h5 fw-bold mt-4 mb-3">Support and dispute resolution</h3>
<p class="mb-3">Our support team is available to answer questions about account setup, deposits, withdrawals, game rules, or technical issues. We respond in English and Indonesian. If a dispute arises—for example, a bet is rejected or a payout seems incorrect—we review the table recording and your account history to resolve it. All session recordings are archived for 90 days.</p>

