<section id="tips" class="section py-5">
<div class="container">
<h2 class="h3 fw-bold mb-4">Getting started on <span class="text-primary fw-black">Robopragma Pro</span></h2>

<h3 class="h5 fw-bold mt-4 mb-3">Account opening and verification</h3>
<p class="mb-3">Open an account by providing your email, creating a password, and confirming your email address. Once confirmed, you can deposit and access games immediately. Before your first withdrawal, complete KYC verification by uploading your national ID, proof of address, and a selfie. Most verifications complete within a few hours to one business day.</p>

<h3 class="h5 fw-bold mt-4 mb-3">Deposit and funding</h3>
<p class="mb-3">Log into your account, navigate to Wallet, and select Deposit. Choose your payment method (DANA, e-wallet, mobile banking, local payment, online payment, e-wallet, or bank transfer). Enter your deposit amount and confirm. Your funds appear in your account balance instantly. Deposit minimums are low—often as little as our welcome offer—so you can start with a modest stake.</p>

<h3 class="h5 fw-bold mt-4 mb-3">Exploring games and tables</h3>
<p class="mb-3">Once funded, navigate to Live Dealer, Slots, Sportsbook, or Esports. Each section displays available games and tables. For live-dealer tables, you see the table limit, number of players, and dealer name. Click Join to take a seat. For slots, click Play to launch the game. For sportsbook and esports, select your market and place your bet.</p>

<h3 class="h5 fw-bold mt-4 mb-3">Withdrawal and account management</h3>
<p class="mb-3">To withdraw, navigate to Wallet and select Withdraw. Enter your withdrawal amount and confirm. The funds are processed to your original payment method, subject to compliance review. Most withdrawals complete within standard business hours. You can also manage your account settings—update your password, enable two-factor authentication, or review your transaction history—from your Account menu.</p>

<ul class="mb-4">
 <li><strong>Enable two-factor authentication:</strong> Protect your account by requiring a code sent to your email or phone before any login from a new device.</li>
 <li><strong>Keep your payment details current:</strong> Update your profile if you change your phone number, email, or bank account so deposits and withdrawals route correctly.</li>
 <li><strong>Review table rules before joining:</strong> Each live-dealer table has a rules panel. Read the payout structure and side-bet options before placing your first bet.</li>
 <li><strong>Contact support if you have questions:</strong> Our team is available to help with account setup, payment issues, game rules, or technical problems.</li>
</ul>

